<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA614_06_IH_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema614_05_ih_0003.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema614_01.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ena614_06">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="4" lang="y" class="is_star">
          <span lang="y">비율이 높은 것부터 차례대로 기호를 써 보세요.</span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box dir_col">
          <div class="drop_info">
            <ul>
              <li>㉠ 0.46</li>
              <li>㉡ 45％</li>
              <li>
                <span>㉢ </span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>12</span>
                  <span>25</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>㉣ 0.5</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="dropdown_area mt_40">
            <div class="dropdown_wrap">
              <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="㉣">
                <option value=""></option>
                <option value="㉠" lang="y">㉠</option>
                <option value="㉡" lang="y">㉡</option>
                <option value="㉢" lang="y">㉢</option>
                <option value="㉣" lang="y">㉣</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="dropdown_wrap">
              <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="㉢">
                <option value=""></option>
                <option value="㉠" lang="y">㉠</option>
                <option value="㉡" lang="y">㉡</option>
                <option value="㉢" lang="y">㉢</option>
                <option value="㉣" lang="y">㉣</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="dropdown_wrap">
              <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="㉠">
                <option value=""></option>
                <option value="㉠" lang="y">㉠</option>
                <option value="㉡" lang="y">㉡</option>
                <option value="㉢" lang="y">㉢</option>
                <option value="㉣" lang="y">㉣</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="dropdown_wrap">
              <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="㉡">
                <option value=""></option>
                <option value="㉠" lang="y">㉠</option>
                <option value="㉡" lang="y">㉡</option>
                <option value="㉢" lang="y">㉢</option>
                <option value="㉣" lang="y">㉣</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <div class="flex gap_4 align_center">
                  <p>㉠ 비율 0.46을 백분율로 나타내면 0.46_100=46 ➔</p>
                  <p>46％입니다</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap_4 align_center">
                  <p>㉢ 비율</p>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>12</span>
                    <span>25</span>
                  </div>
                  <p>를 백분률로 나타내면</p>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>12</span>
                    <span>25</span>
                  </div>
                  <p>×100=48 ➔</p>
                  <p>48％입니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap_4 align_center">
                  <p>
                    ㉣ 비율 0.5를 백분율로 나타내면 0.5_100=0％입니다. <br />
                    50>48>46>45이므로 비율이 높은 것부터 차례대로 기호를 쓰면 ㉣, ㉢, ㉠, ㉡입니다.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
